items.name: Novakid race from StarBound
items.description:
That was more complicated then I expected, but I did it! It's Novakids from starbound!

I had trained 2 LoRas. I tried to make all popular sorts of glyphs on one, but when I did the last version, omega symbol broken the others. First LoRa (v12) was trained on 55 images, and second one (v13) on 63, both on Mistoon Sapphire model.

All glyphs: omega, moon, triangle, rhombus, star, cross, circle, heart, aries.

I tried to add venus and mars symbols, but haven't found enough images.

My recomendation:

Use weights from 0.6 to 0.8.

Use tag glow skin fore more novakids look.

If you want generate characters with omega, triangle, moon or heart symbols, use v13.

If you want generate characters with all glyphs except omega, use v12, but rhombus and circle glyphs may be not stable.

For different types of glyphs use tag <glyph> symbol on face with tag no face or/and faceless.

If you want make random symbol just use tag symbol on face, but SD may generate a brand new symbol.

items.name: Zeitgeist - Semi-Realistic Concept Render (Style LoRa for SDXL)
items.description:
See here for an article about my training method to create near-perfect style and character LoRa's for SDXL 1.0!

I highly recommend using this model with an upscaler workflow. I find that it can greatly increase the already great image quality - depending on the prompt. You can find such an example workflow in the first example image of this post (the one that serves as the thumbnail of this model).

Current version: v1.0 | Recommended weight: 1.0 - or lower when you combine it with other LoRa's | Recommended VAE: SDXL 0.9 | Recommended model: SDXL 1.0 | Recommended settings: 35 steps | DPM++ 2M Karras | CFG 7 | Recommended negative prompt: text, watermark, signature, abstract, burned, instagram, low-quality, low-res, action figure, child drawing, jpeg, low contrast, glossy, puppet, cliché, stock photo, magazine cover (I have done a lot of testing with many dozens of prompt words and this is the best universal negative prompt I could find, all other common negative prompt words people use I found to have no or only a negative effect on the output)

I recommend using the official SDXL 1.0 model that has the SDXL 0.9 VAE already integrated, which you can find here.

Description

A semi-realistic concept render artstyle LoRa for SDXL 1.0, aimed at delivering high-quality 3D renders in the style of Unreal Engine game concept renders and the like.

Trigger words

  • "image in zz artstyle"

Changelog

v1.0

  • Initial release

Additional Info

Credit is not mandatory but I would still appreciate credit when posting images using these LoRa's on social media! Feel free to @ my Twitter and/or Instagram accounts too (@ai_characters)! I would love to know when it is used!

I share all of my model's and training knowledge for free, but donations to my Ko-Fi would be greatly appreciated! Testing so much and training so many model's costs a lot of money.

Feel free to also try out my RVC2 AI voice models which you can find here!

Stats

Dataset:

Training times (for 100 epochs):

  • Artstyle (at 2 repeats): ~1h 30min [???s/it]

Epoch chosen for the final model:

  • 40

items.name: Footjob POV SDXL 1.0
items.description:
Hope you enjoy this LoRA. I recommend using Base SDXL 1.0 as it was trained on that but feel free to try other SDXL versions. Better results if you use resolution 896 x 1152.

FOR the SD 1.5 Version --> (click here)

-FOR USE with keywords: woman, pov, footjob, feet, penis (though just: POV, Footjob is fine)

You can get decent results with just using: POV, footjob if you use Base SDXL with it.

-Negative prompts: text, watermark, logos, extra toes, extra feet, extra penis, blurry, fuzzy

Negative prompts aren't a necessity but can improve quality of life.

-Use Model Strenght 1.0 (if footjobs don't happen anymore go with 1.10-1.50 though avoid 1.5 since it may cause artifacts) if image is too blurry, artifact-ridden or fuzzy stick with 1.0 strength.

Also go with 40 steps or around that and use EULER as a Sampler. Tweak the above values until you find what works for you. Remember it is hard for SD to get feet right so adjust as needed.

This was trained doing 10 epochs and 20 images of POV footjobs. I may train it again upping the steps for better results though I am kinda satisfied with this one.

Feel free to share good images generated with this :)

items.description:
About: Uploaded this outdated model only to archive since this is the very first public model for Asriel Dreemurr, posted originally on certain discord server, it was almost a year ago since I started to learn SD and wondering if was able to train to get some Asriel alternative art. Took me like a whole month of testing and pain since back then it was more frustrating, even using +200 images and 11k steps just few times generated really quite interesting images and it was necessary some inpainting and manual fix, so at this point is totally a waste of time using this

And I lost the prompts for first images since discord decided to erase metadata in all images for no fucking reason, tried to generate couple more but didnt get the same quality from back those days

Highly recommended: Enable highres fix (Denoising strength: 0.6 - 0.9) put in negative prompt: "red pupils, purple fur, (the opposite gender you want to generate)"

Frequently problems: weird poses, double pupils, a weird necklace, gold chains or similar things around the neck, sometimes holding things and too many black lines in the fur or even making some parts of the fur just dark, also wierd clothing, inconsitent faces and almost all time abstract background even if its specified something else


Final disclaimer: Again I dont recomend this one, use only for fun. And tagged as nsfw since it tends to generate that, even prompting like sfw

Landskaper will help you produce better Landscapes (and Seascapes and Cityscapes and so on)!

  • Makes the generated images Sharper

How to use

Just include the LoRA in your generations. Optional: Add the word 'Landskaper' for a slighty bigger effect.

Clip Skip: 1

ENSD: -1

How It was made

Landskaper was made with professional images downloaded from the website, Pexels. The images were cropped, resized and sharpened to improve. Captions were generated using Kohya SS GUI. Finally, the the LoRA was trained using the same GUI. The training took 4..5 hours on my lowly RTX 3060.

items.name: 【再世】next life-柏青
items.description:
这是群星再世第八十二期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

不知道大家是否记得，有一年春晚她和巩汉林合作出演的小品《都市外乡人》，那个有着纯正东北口音的南洋老太太~~~~得啦母鸡，母鸡得啦，参演过《喜临门》、《欢乐家》、《柳树屯》、《手机》、《美丽的契约》、《爱情最美丽》、《邻居也疯狂》、《家事如天》等影视作品，获得过电视电影百合奖、大众电影百花奖。柏青在40余部影视剧中出演老太太，那成熟老道的表演外加慈祥朴实的外形，为她赢得了“关东第一老太”的称号，甘愿当做绿叶陪衬的她，更是深得大众的喜爱。

1996年，柏青从评剧团退休，但没有想到，刚从舞台上退下来的她，却被好朋友张洪杰推荐去了电影《喜莲》的剧组。自此正式步入演艺圈，2003年，在央视黄金时段热播的《希望的田野》，柏青饰演的老太太深深地吸引了巩汉林。当时的巩汉林正在为搭档演员而发愁，再加上赵丽蓉已经去世，这让他也有些迷茫。直到看了柏青的表演，让巩汉林兴奋地大喊：那个老妈妈简直就是赵丽蓉赵妈的翻版，我要立刻去找她。

2014年，柏青因病去世，享年76岁。

2015年，8·12天津滨海新区爆炸事故中，有一位年仅23岁的消防员牺牲，名叫刘程，是柏青的孙子。

items.name: 【再世】next life-姚贝娜
items.description:
这是群星再世第八十三期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

1981年姚贝娜出生于一个富有艺术气息的家庭，父母都是从事艺术相关工作，还有传言说周笔畅的老师就是姚贝娜的父亲，从小受到艺术熏陶的她很喜欢唱歌，父母也培养她的爱好。当大部分孩子还在玩耍的时候，姚贝娜已经在舞台上表演唱歌，展露着自己的音乐天赋，从那以后，她开始频繁地参与各种活动，包括歌曲录制和现场表演，并在各类大型歌唱比赛中收获多项荣誉。16岁就考入了中国音乐学院，每年这个学校只招收十几人，但报名人数却有几万人，但她依旧轻松考过，足见她的能力和潜力。

在大学期间，姚贝娜遇到了马秋华，这是一个在她专业领域中有很高水平的导师，而且还是院长金铁霖的配偶。姚贝娜的亲切和天赋让马秋华对她非常欣赏，因此很快推荐她加入了中国人民解放军海军政治部歌舞团，在那里继续学习不同的音乐知识。有了好老师的引领、自己的不懈努力，姚贝娜可以说把握了事业发展的先机。后来，她为近百部影视剧献唱主题曲，被业界公认为"主题曲皇后"。

2008年获得第十三届CCTV青年歌手电视大奖赛流行唱法金奖，成为青歌赛历史上首位百分冠军 ；同年参加北京奥运会闭幕式的演唱。2012年6月发布个人首张专辑《小头发》 ，同年演唱电视剧《后宫甄嬛传》主题曲《红颜劫》及剧中所有插曲，演唱电影《画皮2》宣传曲《画情》，演唱冯小刚电影《1942》主题曲《生命的河》 。2014年演唱奥斯卡动画《冰雪奇缘》片尾曲《随它吧》…………

2013年参加《中国好声音第二季》，但，被黑幕了

节目组操你妈！那英操你妈！臭傻逼。

2015年，姚贝娜因乳腺癌去世，年仅33岁，

2015年NASA对第41981号小行星已被命名为“姚贝娜”(Yaobeina)，介绍词为：“一位才华横溢充满勇气的中国女歌手，曾因在流行音乐方面造诣屡获奖项。

ps：真不是lora不像，我自认为做人物类型的lora稍微有点经验，但是姚贝娜换个发型就相当于换个脸。。。我问一个是她粉丝的朋友她都懵。

items.description:
LoRA model for Houshou, mother of the navel base, from Kantai Collection.

Recommended settings

  • LoRA network weight around 0.8-0.9

  • Going too low will make it difficult for the k2 sash as well as kimono collar pattern to appear properly.

  • Please generate using highres fix for best effect.

  • Unfortunately due to trying to support multiple concepts, the general aesthetic effect of this LoRA is somewhat poor due to the quality of the underlying dataset. Please use in conjunction with strong aesthetic checkpoints (like Something v2.2) or use detail increasing LoRA (such as more details LoRA)

  • If using with LoRA Block Weights OUTD and OUTALL seem reasonable but I haven't experimented much with other options yet.

Suggested prompts

General appearance/custom outfit tags

1girl, ponytail, hair ribbon, long hair

Base (unremodeled) appearance (green ribbon)

hoshobase, ponytail, pink kimono, anchor symbol, floral print, hair ribbon, (green ribbon), hakama, hakama skirt, ribbon trim, white pantyhose

Increase strength on "green ribbon" if it turns white

Kai Ni appearance (white ribbon, white sash)

hoshokaini, ponytail, pink kimono, anchor symbol, floral print, hair ribbon, white ribbon, (sash), white sash, hakama, hakama skirt, ribbon trim, white pantyhose

Sash can appear in wrong position/not appear at all sometimes, it's a little hit and miss.

Smock/kappougi appearance

((hoshoapr)), ponytail, (apron), (white apron), (white sleeves), anchor symbol, floral print, hair ribbon, (green) ribbon, hakama, hakama skirt, white pantyhose, japanese clothing

Please also add to negative:

pink clothing

I tried riding off of NAI's understanding of aprons, since smock concept is not very strong, and it was...somewhat successful. This outfit is a bit inconsistent, please adjust weights if the outfit does not appear properly.

Optional things to try

yugake, sandals
long hair
black eyes
blue eyes
green eyes
black hair
blue hair
finely detailed iris, detailed eyes

Artists are somewhat split on what Houshou's characteristics are when they depict her.

Detail of eyes suffers somewhat due to the dataset and her tendency to be depicted with Shibafu-style smaller eyes, but YMMV.

Houshou Kai Ni Sen is not properly supported, but if you want Houshou in a green kimono (camo patterns will not fully reproduce)

(((hoshosen))), ponytail, (green kimono), anchor symbol, floral print, hair ribbon, white ribbon, (sash), white sash, hakama, hakama skirt, ribbon trim, white pantyhose, (((multicolored kimono)))

I plan to revise this model later once I acquire better training material to address Houshou K2 Sen kimono pattern issues and general quality issues, but this will take some time as the necessary data does not yet exist publicly.
